text: One Way Ticket () is a 1988 Dominican Republic drama movie directed by Agliberto Meléndez and starring Carlos Alfredo, Ángel Haché, Rafael Villalona, Ángel Muñiz, Víctor Checo, Félix Germán, Frank Lendor. ==Other websites== * Category:1988 drama movies Category:Dominican Republic movies
title: One Way Ticket (1988 movie)
